bilingual.source: He left a note explaining his suicide.
bilingual.target: 他留下了一封解释自己自杀的信。

bilingual.source: Friends tried to stop his suicide attempt.
bilingual.target: 朋友们试图阻止他的自杀企图。

bilingual.source: He was deeply saddened by his friend's suicide.
bilingual.target: 他因朋友的自杀而深感悲痛。

bilingual.source: He committed suicide because of too much pressure.
bilingual.target: 他因为压力太大而自杀了。

bilingual.source: Society needs more resources to prevent suicide.
bilingual.target: 社会需要更多的资源来预防自杀。

bilingual.source: Her family was shocked by her suicide attempt.
bilingual.target: 她的家人对她的自杀企图感到震惊。

bilingual.source: She sought help to prevent her from committing suicide.
bilingual.target: 她寻求帮助以防止自己自杀。

bilingual.source: His family couldn't accept the fact that he committed suicide.
bilingual.target: 他的家人无法接受他自杀的事实。

bilingual.source: After the suicide attempt, she received psychological treatment.
bilingual.target: 自杀企图后，她接受了心理治疗。

bilingual.source: The novel explores the reasons behind the character's suicide.
bilingual.target: 这部小说探讨了角色自杀背后的原因。

list.abstract: Suicide是美国老牌摇滚乐团，是上世纪七十年代初期，阿兰-维嘉与马丁-莱夫一同组建的乐队，他们创造出了一种前所未有无法归类的音乐风格。2016年7月16日，主唱阿兰-维嘉去世，享年七十八岁。

yingyinNormal.en: It'd be a suicide mission.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你这是，自杀行为。

yingyinNormal.en: It's my understanding that it was a suicide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就我理解，那是自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: You know you can't win this. It's suicide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道自己赢不了的，这是自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: With certain obvious exceptions. Suicide, for example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显然也有例外，比如说，自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm basically just on suicide watch. I am not going back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我差不多就是在看着他自杀，我不回去了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mother and Father were terrified. They thought it was a suicide attempt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的父母吓坏了。以为她是想自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Was it an assisted suicide hotline? Your father's home from work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是协助自杀热线吗？你父亲回来了，刚工作完。

yingyinNormal.en: The President of the United States committed suicide? I know it sounds crazy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国总统居然自杀了？我知道这听起来很疯狂

yingyinNormal.en: He's bringing me the police report on Russo's suicide. I'll press him for more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他会把Russo自杀的警方报告拿给我，我尽量多套些信息。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? You know what? That's a lie, I did consider suicide. A lot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道吗？其实……我没说实话，我……我确实想过自杀，很多次。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Reese, I've been looking at these police reports that Fusco sent over, it's possible that suicide wasn't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 里瑟，我看了弗斯科发来的警方报告，有可能不是自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: I was volunteering at a suicide hotline. Get off the couch. Do something with your life!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在一个自杀热线当志愿者，别坐在沙发上了！做点什么改变你的生命吧！

yingyinNormal.en: Was it really a suicide? He's my son. Do you know what prison would do to someone like him? He made a mistake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他真的自杀了吗？他是我儿子。你知道监狱会对他有多大的影响吗？他犯了一个错。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd march into hell for you, if I thought there was a slightest chance of victory. But there isn't, this is suicide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我觉得有半点机会的胜利，我会为你进军地狱，但目前还没有，这是自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I think my mother was too busy planning her suicide to provide saltwater treats. Thank you. So what, you're just never going to tell her?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我妈忙着计划自杀，没空买海滩小吃给我，谢谢，你要告诉她吗？

yingyinNormal.en: At my lowest point, I told my brothe that I was committing suicide even though that wasn't true because I wanted him to be as scared and lonely as I was.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我最低谷的时候，我跟我弟弟说我要自杀，当然那不是真的，我只是想让他和我一样感到恐惧和孤独。

yingyinNormal.en: How much longer? A year since she stopped playing chess and started skipping class, and though her advisor couldn't legally say, I gathered that her erratic behavior culminated in a suicide attempt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多久了？一年前她就不再下棋，开始逃课，虽然她的教授不能明说，不过我猜她甚至曾试图自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's a woman who describes her vows as a suicide flirting with a bridge's edge. And a man who wears his wedding ring as a badge of shame, for the debutante deserved more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个女人将自己的婚誓比作在桥边犹豫自杀的徘徊，和一个将婚戒当作羞耻徽章的男人，因为他觉得配不上这位名媛。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is why I won't condone a mass suicide. If we don't take District 2, we won't get in to the Capitol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我才不允许再发动一次自杀式袭击。如果我们不控制住第二区，我们就无法进入国会区。

yingyinNormal.en: There's a fine line between bravery and suicide, kid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 勇敢和贸然送死是有区别的，小子。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Seymour made the change, went into his backyard, and expressed his displeasure by committing <highlight>suicide</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Seymour 做出了改变，走进他的后院，用自杀来表达他的不满。
